Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.97,0:22:52.89,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2}No time to waste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:52.89,0:22:53.60,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}but make you pace
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.56,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}It's okay to remove, copy, and paste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.56,0:22:56.43,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}I'm doing my way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.31,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}You do it your way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.31,0:22:59.06,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't just follow your left, find the right way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.06,0:22:59.85,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Stereotypes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.85,0:23:00.77,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Too many hypes,
Dialogue: 2,0:23:00.77,0:23:02.48,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}But I'm the epitome of new types
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.48,0:23:03.98,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Having the fear is power to my soul
Dialogue: 2,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.11,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}'Cause I overcome them
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.11,0:23:05.86,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That's how I roll
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.53,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Expose your thoughts
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.53,0:23:10.99,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't be afraid of making mistakes
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.99,0:23:13.41,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Rules prevailing in
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.75,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That may be your greatest rival
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.66,0:23:23.13,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Believe in faith and your heart
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.13,0:23:27.67,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Your true soul stop being in the shades
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.30,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Come on, out in the open sun
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.02,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of the child of destiny
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.69,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Delightful days
Dialogue: 2,0:23:42.06,0:23:46.44,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}are with rich density of love
Dialogue: 2,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.23,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Thorny path
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.24,0:23:53.57,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}There's no easy way for real bliss
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.95,0:23:57.20,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}So I keep on fighting for
Dialogue: 2,0:23:57.20,0:24:01.50,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.16,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Glaciers of ideas, importing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.37,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To my friends, then exporting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To the next, keeping it open
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.83,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We want no closing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Even without those, our thoughts can be duped
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}This mind trade no one can stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}An act of thinking is terrible to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.13,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We just wanna change it up, not drop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}And my crew can rock it like uprock{APPARENTLY A REAL THING: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uprock}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Life is tedious if it ain't flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Copy and paste? Constant defaulting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:16.80,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Put my courage to it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:17.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Begin showing off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}That's the way we wanna live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.68,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep going, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:23.06,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}What was so much of transparency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.69,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Turned into bright expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:34.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Instinct tells me to keep going together, going together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:41.08,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}It's breathtaking moments in life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:48.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Addicted to it, minds craving more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:53.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}I'm believing you and I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:57.26,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We can change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}The sky's the limit, we can spread wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:08.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}to roadless travel, together we go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Persona ability is the power to control one's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the heart is strengthened through bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By becoming involved with others and forming bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were able to obtain the Magician Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power will grow as your bond deepens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I strongly urge you to take this to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I bid you farewell, until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute! Is he yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my parents said to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to be all alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Amagi Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{3:28 Typset - Yasogami High School}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yukiko here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi? Nope, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, on the Midnight Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we were just talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw Yukiko on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen her in that kimono before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{3:57 Typeset - Analog}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wore it during that one interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been texting her, but she hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tried calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just goes straight to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think Amagi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's okay. She's probably just busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or she could've lost her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be busy helping at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drop by the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving? But the bell's about to ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been busy 'cause a group came in without reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it wasn't Amagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that handwriting sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{5:13 Typset - Come on! Join the basketball club!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took notes for Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotcha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful on the way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{5:20 Typset - Go Chess Club | Come on! Join the basketball club! |  Soccer club is currently recruiting!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You the transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you played much basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting if you change your mind, new guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even inexperienced sophomores are welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really crowded today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, try sticking your hand in and calling him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It left bite marks! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chie I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Is this a new game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, does it feel like anyone's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "anyone"? I'm a lonely little bear like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land feels so bear-ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're sure no one's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is running as good as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone showed up on the Midnight Channel yesterday, even though no one's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{6:51 Typeset - Analog}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I'm gonna score myself a hot stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to "Not a Dream, Not a Hoax"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Princess Yukiko's Hunt for Her Prince Charming"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{7:15 Typeset - Princess Yukiko's Hunt for Her Prince Charming!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lacy unmentionables are ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out to catch a whole harem of only the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd taped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{7:57 Typeset - Amagi Family Inn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine by myself. I can hold the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{8:33 Typeset - Useless Laws \N Mr. Experiment}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}High pressure is moving in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}so we should have clear skies all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{8:36 Typeset - Red = L, B = H. Analog \N Today's Weather Forcast}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's see what to expect for the—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be sunny. I should do some laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kept you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found some stuff we can use in my closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura, are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the blades are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one strikes your fancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe both would be good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two suspicious young males found,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one armed with multiple weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you resisting arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't doing anything! We aren't the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just huge sword fanatics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura! Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
