Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}{10:05 Typset - Clockwise, Courage: Mild, Dilligence: Callow, Understanding: Basic, Expression: Rough, Knowledge: Informed}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{10:12 Typset - Currently holding driving awareness week}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys. Don't stir up trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you weren't Dojima's nephew and his friend, you wouldn't have gotten off so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was definitely home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's seen her since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Amagi Yukiko's family asked us to help search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything stick out as unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yukiko seem troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ms. Yamano was staying at the Amagi Inn before the first murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she had some harsh words for the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukiko's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the manager's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's been some theories that she's laying low for some reason or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Yukiko's the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just a rumor floating—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not saying—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You implied Yukiko—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Satonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta save Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this on the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, you should wait out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going! I'm definitely going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she's made up her mind, you can't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, is Amagi in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is onto the scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't run off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko! Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really oblivious of her surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{12:42 Typset - Burning Up}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{12:52 Typset - Burning Up}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rumble, Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke, you've got a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I be "Master"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko... Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Yukiko's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that red looks good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the name Yukiko, meaning "snow child."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow is cold, and it melts quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's transient, worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's perfect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yukiko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Answer me, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Chie told me that red looks good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie was the only one who gave my life meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie is bright and strong, and she can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has everything that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to Chie, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks after my worthless life. Chie is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chie is so kind," huh? What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? {\i1}I'm{\i0} Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm also Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko said that I'm protecting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you gotta love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko's so good-looking, so feminine, so fair-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one all the guys drool over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Yukiko looked at me with such jealousy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, did I get a charge out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Yukiko can't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one standing on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's now how I feel at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, this isn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're just gonna turn your back and deny me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Shadow... The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you're gonna protect the "real" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're gonna pay the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to take good care of Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my footstool, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm the one who can't do anything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yukiko depends on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, don't let her trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!{17:59}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to trick her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true colors, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one all the boys drool over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they represent how you really feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,jealous and envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without me around, she can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be nothing without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my true colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still her friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're right, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the inner "me" that I pretended never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the part of me I couldn't face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously gonna acknowledge my existence and accept me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tear you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear! Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your have established a new bond, allowing you to use another Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You possess the power to wield multiple Personas.{sic, but that's how the game does it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the wild card,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Chosen One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen One?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyro Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No fair! He gets to use two Personas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Persona...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. Yep.{someone in the bg at junes}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko could die the next time it gets foggy over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll need your help to save Amagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of my gratitude, I'll show you something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a fatass and stinks like no other,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's the one who broke the ice and introduced me to Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Next SCENT LOLOLOLOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of these damn chains!
